__TOC__


The purpose of this page is to collect translations for the <nowiki>[[http://bazaar.launchpad.net/~ubuntu-branches/ubuntu/maverick/chromium-browser/maverick/annotate/head:/debian/chromium-browser.desktop|Chromium desktop entry]]</nowiki> in "''Applications > Internet > Chromium Web Browser''" and include them in the code. The reason we must do this is because of the special format Chromium translations use, which does not allow us to use Launchpad or the regular Ubuntu internationalization infrastructure. We've also got a <nowiki>[[https://bugs.edge.launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/chromium-browser/+bug/631670|bug]]</nowiki> to track this.

If the Chromium desktop entry is not translated in your language:

 1. Translate it below, in the '''Add your translations here''' section.
 2. File a request for it to be included by clicking <nowiki>[[https://answers.launchpad.net/ubuntu-translations/+addquestion|here]]</nowiki>.
